  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6323832">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6323832/" class="title-link">好看、写实、不“意淫”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6323832"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bfhz/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48747402-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bfhz/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">北方胡子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-12"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-12 09:55:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6323832_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我非常喜欢看军事小说，前前后后也看过不少，简单来讲我将此书分为两类： 一是“意淫派”的，这类书中作者往往把主角写的非常的牛逼，常常可以创造一个又一个的奇迹，感觉简直不是人，是超人、外星人，感觉这类人的存在的唯一目的就狂虐其它人的，无论是自己人、外国人、外星人...

